      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a fantastic ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I'm selling my trusty car, and it's in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-cared for, runs like a dream, and is just waiting for a new owner to take it out on the road. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. I'm sad to see it go, but I know you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look or have any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
