      "description": "This FD3S chassis remains a quintessential example of 50/50 weight distribution and analog feedback. Powered by the sequential twin-turbocharged 13B-REW rotary, this unit pulls hard through the entire rev range with a seamless transition between the primary and secondary Hitachi turbines. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul with a high-capacity aluminum radiator and a full silicone vacuum line refresh to ensure boost pressure stability. The double-wishbone suspension provides razor-sharp turn-in, and the factory Torsen limited-slip differential remains tight. A mechanically robust specimen for the purist who prioritizes kinematic excellence and rotary reliability.",
